activities:
ArisGlobal collects data for the following purposes: 
1) Registrations/attendance at an ArisGlobal conference or event; 
2) User inquiries and requests for information through emails sent to our sales team; 
3) Participation in interactive discussions and public forums;
4) To provide future services and support to prospective or existing customers;
5) Finalization of contracts / legal requirements with customers
6) To respond to requests for service or quotes for product purchase and Hosted services. Additionally if the customer subscribes for ArisGlobal hosted services, the customer data is hosted on a private, secure and validated Life sciences Cloud at world-class data centers.
